title: [Ta'Illistim, Rocky Trail]
description: Here the weathered rocks provide many hand and footholds for easy climbing.  Cool patches of moss provide relief for sore hands.  The trail above grows steadily steeper as it winds its way up the mountain.  The soft hooting of an owl can be heard in the distance.
